Assemblyman bankrupt, Kelantan's Nenggiri state seat becomes vacantKOTA BARU: The N 43 Nenggiri state seat has been declared vacant after its state assemblyman Datuk Mat Yusof Abdul Ghani was declared a bankrupt.Kelantan State Assembly Speaker Datuk Abdullah Yakub said the Barisan Nasional state assemblyman was declared a bankrupt by the Selangor Insolvency Department on Nov 9 last year.The Speaker’s office only received the bankruptcy notice on May 28 while another notice was sent to the legal adviser office a week earlier, he said.https://sg.news.yahoo.com/assemblyman-bankr...-084117850.htmlNi la masa nak test power, bila lagi? kata BN or PH will take over Kelantan on GE14.
